org.processmining.plugins.etm.experiments

Class StandardLogs

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.processmining.plugins.etm.experiments.StandardLogs

  • public class StandardLogs
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains several static methods to instantly create minimalistic (i.e. only activity and lifecycle attributes) standard event logs

    jbuijs
